Niehu.

767
00:57:54,400 --> 00:57:55,858
Selesaikanlah.

768
00:58:01,234 --> 00:58:03,151
<i>Apa kalian bersenang-senang hari ini?</i>

769
00:58:03,693 --> 00:58:06,401
Ya, tapi aku agak lelah.

770
00:58:09,068 --> 00:58:11,860
Menurutmu apakah pelatih akan marah

771
