01:11:54,421 --> 01:11:56,047
<i>Sudah kubilang aku tidak akan membiarkan</i>

907
01:11:57,088 --> 01:11:58,349
<i>rencanamu berhasil!</i>

908
01:11:59,391 --> 01:12:01,714
Kau akan jatuh bersamaku!

909
01:12:42,469 --> 01:12:43,594
Apa...

910
01:12:46,386 --> 01:12:47,803
Apa ini?

911
01:12:50,720 --> 01:12:52,137
Siapa yang meminta air?

912
01:12:54,221 --> 01:12:55,387
Siapa ini?

913
01:13:28,600 --> 01:13:30,142
Kau takkan bisa lari.

914
01:13:56,155 --> 01:13:57,228
He Ying, kembalilah.

915
01:13:58,020 --> 01:13:59,062
He Ying!

916
